      {
        "id": "2.1",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_neutral.png",
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "So Bob, What's Bitcoin?\nThere's been so much buzz about it lately, with the price increasing!",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2.2",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Bitcoin! It's like digital cash.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_question.png",
          "emotion": "confused",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "digital cash? \nI'm not sure I understand.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2.3",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Think of it like this—imagine sending money to a friend over email, but securely and without needing permission from a bank.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_question.png",
          "emotion": "confused",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Ohhh… so I don’t need a bank app or anything?",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2.4",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Exactly. Bitcoin uses a special network called the blockchain to keep track of who owns what. It’s public, but super secure.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_listening.png",
          "emotion": "listening",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2.5",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.5",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_holding_phone.png",
          "emotion": "listening",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...hold on, I'm getting a message",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_asking.png",
          "emotion": "question",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Wait, blockchain? I’ve heard that word thrown around, but I don’t really get it.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "2.6",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "2.6",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Picture a notebook that everyone can see, but no one can erase or fake. Every time someone sends Bitcoin, a new line gets written. That notebook? That’s the blockchain.",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_listening.png",
          "emotion": "listening",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": "blockchain-diagram"
      },
      {
        "id": "3.1",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "3.1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_neutral.png",
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_shocked.png",
          "emotion": "shocked",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Okay, but how does it stay safe? Can’t someone just copy the cash?",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": null
      },
      {
        "id": "3.2",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "3.2",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Good question! Think of it as a public, digital diary of all Bitcoin transactions. Once something’s written, it’s locked in!",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_listening.png",
          "emotion": "listening",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": "bitcoin-padlock"
      },
      {
        "id": "3.3",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "3.3",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_neutral.png",
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "...",
          "size": "small"
        },
        "rightCharacter": {
          "image": "carol_understanding.png",
          "emotion": "understanding",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "So it’s like a diary no one can erase?",
          "size": "large"
        },
        "centralDialogue": {
          "active": false,
          "content": ""
        },
        "visualAid": "null"
      },
      {
        "id": "3.4",
        "storyNumber": 1,
        "sceneNumber": "3.4",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "cafe",
        "leftCharacter": {
          "image": "bob_explaining.png",
          "emotion": "explaining",
          "dialogueActive": true,
          "dialogue": "Exactly. Each new page—aka ‘block’—is locked to the previous one. It’s like a chain of events no one can change!",
          "size": "small"
